commentAnnotations.text: For asymptomatic amylase and/or lipase elevations refer to Table 6-18
Placebo administrations to those patients randomized to the placebo arm will stop after unblinding.
Safety and survival follow ups will not be needed for patients who transfer to Post-Trial Access (PTA).

studyDefinitionDocumentVersions.description: Revised end of study definition for PTA, updated HLH safety info, and public health emergency mitigation.
Continuation of study following final PFS analysis to characterize OS benefit; mandatory unblinding.
Adjusted timing of final PFS analysis and included interim PFS analysis based on delayed treatment effect.
Aligned contraception requirements and updated GDPR personal data definitions.
